{"tid":1532523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"螢光粉抹落鈔票度    會唔會影響檢測銀紙真偽嘅準確性","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:34:10.000Z","uid":100761,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f260db3027683b790ab612c695103cf71218f77a","tid":1532523,"uid":100761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:15:31.000Z","msg":"如題  今日見到幾個post 話有螢光粉 <br />\n突然諗到 啲鋪頭驗鈔嗰時又係會拎啲燈係度照照照<br />\n假設真係有直升機灑螢光粉灑到成件衫都係 <br />\n而有人拎張銀紙係度hi hi hi  係冇放入自己銀包嘅情況下撚手就用埋佢<br />\n咁樣啲粉咪好快傳到成香港都係囉? <br />\n<br />\n但係驗鈔又係用燈照  呢啲粉又係用燈照 <br />\n驗鈔機啲燈會唔會照到（而家傳緊 未完全確定有冇出現過嘅）呢啲螢光粉<br />\n同埋咁樣會唔會影響檢測銀紙真偽嘅準確性呢? <br />\n求專家解答"},{"pid":"ec6bff0bdf047a545c009db3c9265b666ba7b9fc","tid":1532523,"uid":100761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"自推一下  求解答"},{"pid":"503815ac8e60837a6f1c889eda4cf94a6e053694","tid":1532523,"uid":100761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:16:23.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"d2cd4de09c74bfd13d0179695c6f6600d15f7ca0","tid":1532523,"uid":100761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:16:34.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"9c5281c11b37c010d398b2e58175c7d8e92b8bdd","tid":1532523,"uid":100761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"100d40a7c13062a63702314baebb3ff9f18ec37c","tid":1532523,"uid":100761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:17:13.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"9574a16804ffdd1da80b5bbe9bc603847aa8a26d","tid":1532523,"uid":113074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:17:46.000Z","msg":"睇片嗰啲唔係粉<br />\n好強黏性同快乾"},{"pid":"d4e9805625f57f198885523a61e38d8bf320565d","tid":1532523,"uid":100761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:17:57.000Z","msg":"6 咁政府係咪先係攬抄專家呢"},{"pid":"8c493191e5c8f5692f169f978975f3f1bd4166e8","tid":1532523,"uid":100761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite